FBIS4-28870 "dreas114_c_94019" FBIS-EAS-94-114 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 North Korea PRC Trade Union Leader Receives DPRK Counterpart PRC Trade Union Leader Receives DPRK Counterpart SK1006035294 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network in Korean 0100 GMT 10 Jun 94 SK1006035294 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network in Korean 0100 GMT 10 Jun 94 Korean BFN [Text] Comrade Wei Jianxing, member of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee and member of the CPC Central Committee Secretariat and president of All-China Federation of Trade Unions, on 7 June met with a delegation of the Federation of Trade Unions of Korea, which is visiting China, led by Chu Song-il, chairman of the federation. During the meeting, Comrade Wei Jianxing stressed that the blood-tied China-DPRK friendship is a friendship that has overcome the trials of history.
